# 🚀 Git & GitHub Tutorial

Welcome! This tutorial is your step-by-step guide to understanding how to use **Git** for version control and **GitHub** for collaboration and hosting code.

---

## 📌 What’s the Difference?

| Git          | GitHub                     |
|--------------|----------------------------|
| Local tool   | Cloud platform             |
| Tracks code history | Hosts repositories online |
| Works offline | Needs internet            |
| CLI-based    | Web-based UI + CLI support |

---

## 🛠️ Installing Git

- **Windows**: [Download Git](https://git-scm.com/download/win)
- **Mac**: Use Homebrew → `brew install git`
- **Linux**: Use apt → `sudo apt install git`

Verify installation:
```bash
git --version
